{"tid":2329400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓據報買俄羅斯疫苗 金正恩料不會接種","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T12:11:01.000Z","uid":295230,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4f99f68735767c3993a228c9fe72c999a78d6f","tid":2329400,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"疫情全球大流行，多間藥廠研發新冠肺炎疫苗，北韓一直聲稱「零確診」，但似乎仍與爆疫國家般渴求新冠疫苗。據早前有媒體報道指，中國已向北韓領袖金正恩及其家人提供新冠疫苗。日本媒體周二報道指，北韓已購買俄羅斯的新冠疫苗，北韓高官已開始接種。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》引述消息人士指，北韓已從俄羅斯購買疫苗，相信該款疫苗為「史普尼克5號」（Sputnik V）<br />\n<br />\n《朝日新聞》報道指，暫未知道北韓的購買規模。對於金正恩會否接種該款疫苗，消息人士則指，在安全性尚未確認的階段，估計金正恩不會接種。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯官方早前指出，「史普尼克5號」的效用率高達96%，而且餘下4%人士縱染上新冠肺炎，也會只有輕微的流鼻涕、咳嗽及發燒，肺部卻沒有受損。不過，普京至今尚未接種俄羅斯新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n驚死到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de957d2e611e693438f523c11b15ac14ba4cc10","tid":2329400,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2830009/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%B2%B7%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%20%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%96%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2830009%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%2520%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%2581%25A9%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28YICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=aff39665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2830009/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E8%B2%B7%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%20%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E6%96%99%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE</a>"},{"pid":"0778e40d1da45068f294c5e2e951d7eec4808845","tid":2329400,"uid":39871,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔買中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1b550a443a118d04eadc71813b424452ff120c","tid":2329400,"uid":57554,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0778e40d1da45068f294c5e2e951d7eec4808845","tid":2329400,"uid":39871,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔買中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"恩仔知中共啲嘢閪硬<br />\n<br />\n美國佬一黎唔會供貨，二黎恩仔好難同國民交代。<br />\n<br />\n所以係得俄佬貨可以用。"},{"pid":"7321d683732eb4bcfdd02d6340f6f37720678814","tid":2329400,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1184555e559b3982fb4981cf04b5bd3b1b8422bf","tid":2329400,"uid":183090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e1b550a443a118d04eadc71813b424452ff120c","tid":2329400,"uid":57554,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0778e40d1da45068f294c5e2e951d7eec4808845","tid":2329400,"uid":39871,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:13:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔買中國疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"恩仔知中共啲嘢閪硬<br />\n<br />\n美國佬一黎唔會供貨，二黎恩仔好難同國民交代。<br />\n<br />\n所以係得俄佬貨可以用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:35:33.000Z","msg":"典型北韓官員同支那人一𨳊樣，口裡講到英美點點點，到最後要用，都係用外國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid